519
00:33:17,953 --> 00:33:19,048
Yoo Jenny.

520
00:33:19,852 --> 00:33:21,288
Di mana Yoo Jenny?

521
00:33:21,822 --> 00:33:24,723
Jenny dan Ro Na tidak ada di sini.

522
00:33:24,723 --> 00:33:27,487
