00:41:13,543 --> 00:41:15,543
Dia kehilangan kesempatannya secara adil.

658
00:41:15,543 --> 00:41:18,013
Bukankah kau harus memberinya kesempatan?

659
00:41:18,013 --> 00:41:21,138
Apa kau peduli kepada Jenny?

660
00:41:21,584 --> 00:41:24,608
Apa yang dia katakan?

661
00:41:25,853 --> 00:41:28,184
Apa kau belum sadar?

662
00:41:28,184 --> 00:41:30,554
